  "prompt": "What can you say about my birth chart ?",
  "response": "To provide insights about your birth chart, I would need your date, time, and place of birth. A birth chart, also known as a natal chart, is a map of where all the planets were in their journey around the Sun at the exact moment you were born. It can offer insights into your personality, strengths, challenges, and life path.\n\nIf you're comfortable sharing your birth information, please do, and I'll provide a general overview based on the key components of your chart, such as your Sun, Moon, and Rising signs. If you prefer not to share this info, I can explain the significance of different aspects of a birth chart in a general sense.",
